short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Nuxt Assistant for cozy debugging Nuxt sites

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Enhance your Nuxt.js debugging experience with "Nuxt Assistant" - a powerful extension designed specifically for developers working with the Nuxt.js framework in production environments. This extension seamlessly integrates into your Chrome DevTools, offering a dedicated panel filled with insights and tools to boost your productivity. Please note, this extension is compatible only with Nuxt 3 and Nuxt 4
